Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 152 Samborski Drive is a rare southwest opportunity located just outside of Winnipeg in the R.M. of MacDonald. The site has easy access to McGillivray Boulevard and is a 2-minute drive to Kenaston Boulevard, and a 7-minute drive to Perimeter Highway.

165 Centennaire Drive offers an excellent low-cost, well-lit and functional warehouse solution in the Portage La Prairie region. It is easily accessible by truck and offers dock and drive-in level overhead doors to accommodate all loading functions. Two levels of office space, totaling over 4,000 square feet, provides all the administrative space most users would require. Additionally, there is more than sufficient parking space. With an expiry date of December 31, 2023, there is no long term lease requirement.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Warehouse for Lease in Southport, MB
